---

---

<section class="section section--tinted" id="como-donar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <h2 class="section-title">¿Cómo Donar?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto">
        Un proceso simple y seguro que salva vidas.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <article class="step-card">
        <div class="step-card__icon">
          <svg
            width="28"
            height="28"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#bc002d"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path
              d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"
            ></path><rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="4" rx="1"></rect><path
              d="M9 14l2 2 4-4"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="step-card__title">1. Consulta los Requisitos</h3>
        <p class="step-card__desc">
          Verifica condiciones básicas de salud, edad y peso antes de asistir.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="step-card">
        <div class="step-card__icon">
          <svg
            width="28"
            height="28"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#bc002d"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line
              x1="16"
              y1="2"
              x2="16"
              y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line
              x1="3"
              y1="10"
              x2="21"
              y2="10"></line></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="step-card__title">2. Agenda tu Cita</h3>
        <p class="step-card__desc">
          Encuentra tu centro de donación o unidad móvil más cercana y reserva
          tu lugar.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="step-card">
        <div class="step-card__icon">
          <svg
            width="28"
            height="28"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#bc002d"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path
              d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="step-card__title">3. Salva Vidas</h3>
        <p class="step-card__desc">
          Asiste a tu cita y ayuda hasta a 3 pacientes con una sola donación.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .step-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: #fff0ef;
    border: 1px solid #e4bdbc;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-card__icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: rgba(188, 0, 45, 0.1);
  }

  .step-card__title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #281717;
  }

  .step-card__desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #5c403f;
  }
</style>
